* What's this:

It's Firefox search plugins for Arch Linux users.

This repository include three add-on:

1. Arch Linux Package Database Search
file   : archlinux-package_database.xml
release: https://addons.mozilla.org/ja/firefox/addon/archlinux-packa
engine : https://www.archlinux.org/packages/

2. Arch Linux AUR Search
file   : archlinux-AUR.xml
release: https://addons.mozilla.org/ja/firefox/addon/archlinux-aur/
engine : https://aur.archlinux.org/

3. Arch Linux Wiki Search
file   : archlinux-wiki.xml
release: https://addons.mozilla.org/ja/firefox/addon/archlinux-wiki/
engine : https://wiki.archlinux.org/

You can search these Arch Linux resources to quickly and easily with firefox if you want.

